        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500">Adani's Bhutan Project for ‘Mindfulness City’</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Gautam Adani is <a href="https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/investing/commodities/2024/10/30/gautam-adani-vies-for-projects-in-bhutans-mindfulness-city-in-overseas-push/#:~:text=(Bloomberg)%20%2D%2D%20Billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani,its%20southern%20border%20with%20India." target="_blank">exploring</a> investment in Bhutan’s new Gelephu “Mindfulness City,” a mega township development project. Adani Group is in talks with Bhutan’s government to establish solar and hydroelectric power plants in the region. This venture aligns with the conglomerate’s green energy focus and broader strategy of international expansion, adding to its ongoing projects in Asia, Africa, and the Middle East. Besides renewable energy, the city plans to include an international airport and dry port, with construction likely beginning in mid-2024. The city’s eco-friendly infrastructure is set to make Bhutan a sustainable economic hub.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
